cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a deep learning method for vision applications that combines generative and discriminative approaches to improve the accuracy of predicting ordinary labels using complementary labels. This work is highly relevant to the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE).
